title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-10-2013 TUES
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show DEC-10-2013 TUES






The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET


        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/10/13Tuesday, December 10, 2013 10:59 AM





What timeless classic movie has a Christmas theme that 

      doesn't seem like a Christmas movie at all...Glenn explains.


  Also, the coldest temperature ever recorded has just been reached,
         even though according to some temperatures are rising according to global warm.


  Plus, writer and columnist Michelle Malkin joins the program to give her review
           of Glenn's Miracles and Massacres, 


          and the guys discuss the president's inappropriate behavior at Nelson Mandela's funeral.
